        <owl:Class rdf:about="http://dbpedia.org/ontology/BasketballLeague">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="es">liga de baloncesto</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="fr">ligue de basketball</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="en">basketball league</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="ur">ШЁШ§ШіЪ©Щ№ ШЁШ§Щ„ Ъ©ЫҢ Ш§ЩҶШ¬Щ…ЩҶ</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="ko">лҶҚкө¬ лҰ¬к·ё</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="el">ОҹОјОҝПғПҖОҝОҪОҙОҜОұ ОҡОұО»ОұОёОҝПғПҶОұОҜПҒО№ПғО·ПӮ</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="de">Basketball-Liga</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="ja">гғҗгӮ№гӮұгғғгғҲгғңгғјгғ«гғӘгғјгӮ°</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="ga">sraith cispheile</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="nl">basketbal competitie</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="it">lega di pallacanestro</rdfs:label><rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">a group of sports teams that compete against each other in Basketball</rdfs:comment><rdfs:comment xml:lang="ur">Ъ©ЪҫЫҢЩ„ЩҲЪә Ъ©ЫҢ Щ№ЫҢЩ…ЩҲЪә Ъ©Ш§ Ш§ЫҢЪ© ЪҜШұЩҲЩҫ Ш¬ЩҲ ШЁШ§ШіЪ©Щ№ ШЁШ§Щ„ Щ…ЫҢЪә Ш§ЫҢЪ© ШҜЩҲШіШұЫ’ ШіЫ’ Щ…ЩӮШ§ШЁЩ„ЫҒ Ъ©ШұШӘШ§ ЫҒЫ’</rdfs:comment><rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://dbpedia.org/ontology/SportsLeague"/><prov:wasDerivedFrom rdf:resource="http://mappings.dbpedia.org/index.php/OntologyClass:BasketballLeague"/>
        </owl:Class><owl:Class rdf:about="http://dbpedia.org/ontology/NaturalEvent">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="fr">Г©vГ©nement naturel</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="en">natural event</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="ur">ЩӮШҜШұШӘЫҢ ЩҲШ§ЩӮШ№ЫҒ</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="el">ПҶП…ПғО№ОәПҢ ОіОөОіОҝОҪПҢПӮ</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="de">Naturereignis</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="nl">gebeurtenis in de natuur</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="it">evento naturale</rdfs:label><rdfs:comment xml:lang="el">ОӨОҝ ПҶП…ПғО№ОәПҢ ОіОөОіОҝОҪПҢПӮ ПҮПҒО·ПғО№ОјОҝПҖОҝО№ОөОҜП„ОұО№ ОіО№Оұ ОҪОұ ПҖОөПҒО№ОіПҒО¬ПҲОөО№ ОӯОҪОұ ПғП…ОјОІО¬ОҪ ПҖОҝП… ПҖПҒОұОіОјОұП„ОҝПҖОҝО№ОөОҜП„ОұО№ ПҶП…ПғО№ОәО¬</rdfs:comment><rdfs:comment xml:lang="ur">Щ…Ш§ШҜЫҢ ШӘЩӮШұЫҢШЁ Ъ©Ш§ Ш§ШіШӘШ№Щ…Ш§Щ„ ЩӮШҜШұШӘЫҢ Ш·ЩҲШұ ЩҫШұ ШұЩҲЩҶЩ…Ш§ ЫҒЩҲЩҶЫ’ ЩҲШ§Щ„Ы’ ЩҲШ§ЩӮШ№Ы’ Ъ©ЩҲ ШЁЫҢШ§ЩҶ Ъ©ШұЩҶЫ’ Ъ©Ы’ Щ„ЫҢЫ’ Ъ©ЫҢШ§ Ш¬Ш§ШӘШ§ ЫҒЫ’Ы”</rdfs:comment><rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Event"/><prov:wasDerivedFrom rdf:resource="http://mappings.dbpedia.org/index.php/OntologyClass:NaturalEvent"/>
        </owl:Class><owl:Class rdf:about="http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Province">
