        <rdfs:label xml:lang="es">actor porno</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="fr">acteur porno/acteur adulte</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="en">adult (pornographic) actor</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="ur">ШЁШ§Щ„Шә Ш§ШҜШ§Ъ©Ш§Шұ</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="ko">м„ұмқё л°°мҡ°</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="el">ОөОҪО®О»О№ОәОұПӮ (ПҖОҝПҒОҪОҝОіПҒОұПҶО№ОәПҢПӮ) О·ОёОҝПҖОҝО№ПҢПӮ</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="pt">ator adulto</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="pl">aktor pornograficzny</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="de">pornographischer Schauspieler</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="gl">actor porno</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="ja">гғқгғ«гғҺеҘіе„Ә</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="ga">aisteoir pornagrafaГӯochta</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="zh">иүІжғ…жј”е“Ў</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="nl">pornografisch acteur</rdfs:label><rdfs:label xml:lang="it">attore porno</rdfs:label><rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A pornographic actor or actress or a porn star is a person who performs sex acts in film, normally characterised as a pornographic film.</rdfs:comment><rdfs:comment xml:lang="gl">Un actor ou unha actriz porno ou pornogrГЎfico/a, Г© un actor ou actriz de cine porno que actГәa en pelГӯculas de temГЎtica pornogrГЎfica..&amp;lt;ref&amp;gt;https://gl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Actor_pornogr%C3%A1fico&amp;lt;/ref&amp;gt;</rdfs:comment><rdfs:comment xml:lang="ur">Ш§ЫҢЪ© ЩҒШӯШҙ Ш§ШҜШ§Ъ©Ш§Шұ ЫҢШ§ Ш§ШҜШ§Ъ©Ш§ШұЫҒ ЫҢШ§ ЩҫЩҲШұЩҶ ШіЩ№Ш§Шұ ЩҲЫҒ ШҙШ®Шө ЫҒЩҲШӘШ§ ЫҒЫ’ Ш¬ЩҲ ЩҒЩ„Щ… Щ…ЫҢЪә Ш¬ЩҶШіЫҢ ШӯШұЪ©ШӘЫҢЪә Ъ©ШұШӘШ§ ЫҒЫ’ШҢ Ш№Ш§Щ… Ш·ЩҲШұ ЩҫШұ Ш§ШіЫ’ ЩҒШӯШҙ ЩҒЩ„Щ… Ъ©Ы’ Ш·ЩҲШұ ЩҫШұ ШҜЫҢЪ©ЪҫШ§ Ш¬Ш§ШӘШ§ ЫҒЫ’Ы”</rdfs:comment><rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Actor"/><owl:equivalentClass rdf:resource="http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q488111"/><prov:wasDerivedFrom rdf:resource="http://mappings.dbpedia.org/index.php/OntologyClass:AdultActor"/>
